{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d1e7f62ec3","title":"给彭真的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5d9ca82d7a","index":0,"year":1962,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"d1e7f62ec3"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5fd56865b0","name":"彭真","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"420d6f45f9","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记。"},{"id":"509fc273c6","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"巴基斯坦驻华大使是毕尔·阿里·穆军默德·拉希迪，毛泽东1962年7月15日在北京会见了他。卡博代表团指阿尔巴尼亚劳动党中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记卡博率领的阿尔巴尼亚劳动党代表团，毛泽东于1962年6月29日在武汉东湖宾馆会见了他们。"}],"contents":[{"id":"205d96a1e1","type":"title","text":"给彭真的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3"},{"id":"420d6f45f9","type":"paragraph","text":"彭真同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3"},{"id":"509fc273c6","type":"paragraph","text":"我现决定在武汉住到月底，游长江对我十分有益，我要游七天至十天江。然后直返北京。因此巴基斯坦大使，卡博代表团，都在武昌谈话。P请你安排。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3"},{"id":"f4c473c6cd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3"},{"id":"ddcce6f374","type":"paragraph","text":"二十二日上午四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3"}],"page":{"id":"f68b84c87d","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"d1e7f62ec3","start":159,"end":159}}}},"__N_SSG":true}